---
title: Beef Rump & Creamy Parmesan Sauce with Shortcut Garlic Potatoes & Cherry Tomato Salad
description: A perfectly cooked steak is the ultimate go-to meal when you want to impress but you’ve got to be quick- all it needs is five minutes in the pan and five minutes to rest. Serve it with simple sides, and you’ll have a gourmet meal on the table in no time!
